# Anaj Bahi - environment configuration
#
# Phase 1 (the current build) is a LOCAL-ONLY offline PWA. It needs NO secrets,
# NO API keys, and NO .env file at all. You can run the whole app with just:
#
#     cd frontend && pnpm install && pnpm dev
#
# The variables below are documented here for the LATER Phase-4 cloud-sync/backup
# backend (FastAPI + Postgres, under backend/). They are NOT required until then.
#
# --- Phase 4 (cloud sync backend) - not needed yet ---
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql+psycopg://user:password@localhost:5432/anajbahi
# DEVICE_SYNC_TOKEN=replace-with-a-long-random-token
